---
title: Sweet Chilli Beef Bao Buns with Crushed Spring Onion Potatoes & Asian Slaw
description: Sweet chilli-glazed beef rissoles nestled within the fluffiest of bao buns - does it get any better than this? With the addition of crushed potatoes and a crunchy, crispy slaw on the side, we can confirm it does!

*We’ve replaced the
parsley in this recipe
with mint due to local
ingredient availability.
It’ll be just as
delicious, just follow
your recipe card!*
